18
00:01:11,610 --> 00:01:14,330
So, it
actually cools the low-temperature region

19
00:01:14,330 --> 00:01:18,960
and heats the high-temperature region.

20
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:23,180
A backward-running heat engine is a refrigeration
machine, but its technical name

21
00:01:23,180 --> 00:01:25,540
